081802 PHASE 3 start. Goal: thin Dockerfile COPYs the embedded static-linux payload (server+helpers) into the image instead of compiling them (drop golang builder stage + toolchain runtime base). Plan: (3a) init dumps embedded linux payload into the build context (compose mode); (3b) rewrite Dockerfile template -> slim base + apt/node/agents + COPY binaries; fall back to source-compile when linux payload absent (darwin CLI pre-multi-arch); (3c) golden-update + verify. Verification note: full docker build is slow/network-heavy; will rely on golden + structural checks, offer real build.
